<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 18:09:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>真主党袭击以色列国防军北部基地，在黎巴嫩南部上空击落以色列无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-northern-idf-base-downs-israeli-drone-over-southern-lebanon/0000018f-d4b7-dd44-a3ef-d7b726920000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，这架无人机是在距以色列边境约12英里处使用地对空导弹拦截的，并正在调查这一事件。以色列北部火箭弹袭击后，多个地点发生火灾</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-northern-idf-base-downs-israeli-drone-over-southern-lebanon/0000018f-d4b7-dd44-a3ef-d7b726920000</guid></item><item><title>数千名以色列人抗议内塔尼亚胡联盟，要求在拜登的加沙提议中达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-netanyahu-coalition-demand-hostage-deal-amid-bidens-gaza-proposal/0000018f-d46f-d673-ab8f-f7efb8030000</link><description>人质家属在各个城市和内阁部长的家中领导抗议活动，推动美国人质协议获得批准和以色列提前选举；一名人质的母亲表示，拜登发表讲话“因为他知道内塔尼亚胡可以破坏这笔交易”。三名抗议者在以色列北部被捕</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:18:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-netanyahu-coalition-demand-hostage-deal-amid-bidens-gaza-proposal/0000018f-d46f-d673-ab8f-f7efb8030000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，第 239 天：拜登宣布停火、人质协议的三阶段提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-239-biden-announces-three-stage-proposal-for-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018f-d49f-d5bc-a1bf-dfbf8d400000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登宣布三阶段停火协议提案 ■ 消息人士称，哈马斯的官方答复将取决于加沙酋长叶海亚·辛瓦尔和穆罕默德·代夫 ■ 以色列国防军表示，其空袭杀死了加沙的三名哈马斯关键成员 ■ 内塔尼亚胡正式受邀向国会发表讲话■ 战争进入 239 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 17:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-239-biden-announces-three-stage-proposal-for-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018f-d49f-d5bc-a1bf-dfbf8d400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察“打击犯罪分子”，骚扰贝都因村居民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-operating-against-criminals-harasses-residents-of-bedouin-village/0000018f-d081-d5bc-a1bf-dfb1d5620000</link><description>内盖夫塔拉宾萨纳的一名居民表示，“他们在这里所做的不是法律，而是灌输恐怖”。当每次外出都有被逮捕或罚款的风险时，许多社区成员因警察的存在而不敢离开家</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 15:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-operating-against-criminals-harasses-residents-of-bedouin-village/0000018f-d081-d5bc-a1bf-dfb1d5620000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的提议是与以色列协调的；美国担心内塔尼亚胡极右翼盟友的强烈反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/biden-deal-was-coordinated-with-israel-u-s-fears-backlash-by-netanyahu-far-right-allies/0000018f-d416-d513-a9af-f67694290000</link><description>以色列和美国高级官员表示，拜登团队在演讲前通知了以色列、卡塔尔和埃及，试图避免上个月提案中缺乏协调的情况。一位美国官员表示，“内塔尼亚胡仍然可以制造困难，但他最初的反应令人鼓舞”</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 15:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/biden-deal-was-coordinated-with-israel-u-s-fears-backlash-by-netanyahu-far-right-allies/0000018f-d416-d513-a9af-f67694290000</guid></item><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦抗议者占领布鲁克林博物馆的部分区域</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/pro-palestinian-protesters-occupy-parts-of-brooklyn-museum/0000018f-d338-d5bc-a1bf-df389f580000</link><description>逮捕了一些人，但纽约警察局发言人表示，在抗议结束之前不会有正式的统计</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 10:28:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/pro-palestinian-protesters-occupy-parts-of-brooklyn-museum/0000018f-d338-d5bc-a1bf-df389f580000</guid></item><item><title>除辛贝特外，警察局长还计划为内塔尼亚胡家族设立私人保安部门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/police-chief-plans-private-security-unit-for-netanyahu-family-in-addition-to-shin-bet/0000018f-d2c0-d513-a9af-f6f0f6b60000</link><description>据第 12 频道报道，专员 Kobi Shabtai 解释说，由于针对总理的抗议活动日益增多，警察捉襟见肘，因此有必要设立这个新单位吗？</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 08:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/police-chief-plans-private-security-unit-for-netanyahu-family-in-addition-to-shin-bet/0000018f-d2c0-d513-a9af-f6f0f6b60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡拒绝加沙永久停火；甘茨要求召开紧急战时内阁会议讨论拜登协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article-live/hamas-ready-to-deal-positively-with-proposal-that-includes-a-permanent-gaza-cease-fire/0000018f-d178-d673-ab8f-f7f89e9b0000</link><description>人质家属：拜登发表讲话，因为他知道内塔尼亚胡可能破坏协议 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部称，一名青少年在约旦河西岸被以色列军队射杀 ■ 真主党火箭弹袭击了以色列北部的以色列国防军基地；在黎巴嫩上空击落一架以色列国防军无人机 ■ 卡塔尔哈马斯领导层表示支持停火提议，等待辛瓦尔和德伊夫在加沙的表态</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 01:55:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article-live/hamas-ready-to-deal-positively-with-proposal-that-includes-a-permanent-gaza-cease-fire/0000018f-d178-d673-ab8f-f7f89e9b0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列不能错过另一个与沙特阿拉伯关系正常化的机会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-miss-yet-another-opportunity-to-normalize-ties-with-saudi-arabia/0000018f-cfdb-dd44-a3ef-cfdbc2c90000</link><description>这并不是以色列第一次放弃与沙特建立关系的机会。但这一次，说“不”就意味着拒绝冲出我们的贫民窟并作为合作伙伴和盟友进入该地区的机会</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 21:11:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israel-cant-miss-yet-another-opportunity-to-normalize-ties-with-saudi-arabia/0000018f-cfdb-dd44-a3ef-cfdbc2c90000</guid></item><item><title>美国国会领导人正式邀请内塔尼亚胡在国会联席会议上发表讲话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/u-s-congressional-leaders-invite-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018f-d021-dbdb-a59f-d1690b560000</link><description>包括查克·舒默在内的国会领导人正式邀请内塔尼亚胡在国会发表讲话，该讲话已经引起民主党议员的强烈反对，其中许多人发誓要抵制以色列在加沙战争中的行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 20:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/u-s-congressional-leaders-invite-netanyahu-to-address-joint-session-of-congress/0000018f-d021-dbdb-a59f-d1690b560000</guid></item><item><title>在希伯伦，巴勒斯坦人现在渴望实行 10 月 7 日之前存在的种族隔离制度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hebron-palestinians-now-long-for-apartheid-as-it-existed-before-october-7/0000018f-cfe6-d5bc-a1bf-dff672570000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，希伯伦巴勒斯坦人的生活就不一样了。经过两个月几乎完全封锁后，他们现在每天晚上 7 点到早上 7 点都被限制在家里。以色列士兵和定居者的错误逮捕、暴力和羞辱是他们每天的遭遇</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 19:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-hebron-palestinians-now-long-for-apartheid-as-it-existed-before-october-7/0000018f-cfe6-d5bc-a1bf-dff672570000</guid></item><item><title>拜登敦促哈马斯接受以色列全面的新停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-comprehensive-new-israeli-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-cfcd-d5bc-a1bf-dffd47550000</link><description>根据拜登提出的以色列三阶段提案，总统敦促以色列拒绝内部压力，不要错过支持“不明的全面胜利概念”的时机</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/biden-urges-hamas-to-accept-comprehensive-new-israeli-cease-fire-proposal/0000018f-cfcd-d5bc-a1bf-dffd47550000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨在政府任职逾期，现在内塔尼亚胡已经不在乎他笨拙的操纵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/gantz-overstayed-in-the-govt-now-netanyahu-doesnt-care-about-his-clumsy-maneuvering/0000018f-ce78-dc8d-a18f-fffdda840000</link><description>诚然，随着加沙战事的持续，甘茨在战时内阁中的地位日趋软弱，而且他威胁要在 6 月 8 日之前辞职的威胁看起来是经过深思熟虑的。但内塔尼亚胡可能严重低估了以色列人对其总理的不满</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:27:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/gantz-overstayed-in-the-govt-now-netanyahu-doesnt-care-about-his-clumsy-maneuvering/0000018f-ce78-dc8d-a18f-fffdda840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军将军巴拉克·希拉姆 (Barak Hiram) 是谁？他下令用坦克向基布兹一处房屋开火，里面有 13 名人质？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/who-is-the-idf-general-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-a-kibbutz-home-with-13-hostages-inside/0000018f-ca16-da41-a9cf-db3eaa080000</link><description>双桅船。巴拉克·希拉姆将军在 10 月 7 日的战斗中发出了最具争议的命令：向哈马斯恐怖分子扣押人质的贝埃里基布兹房屋发射坦克炮弹。与认识这位勇敢、鹰派军官的人交谈后，我们发现他是一个打破成见的人。这是以色列国防军的新面孔吗？</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:23:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/who-is-the-idf-general-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-a-kibbutz-home-with-13-hostages-inside/0000018f-ca16-da41-a9cf-db3eaa080000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 238 天：法国因拉法行动禁止以色列公司参加军火博览会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-238-france-bans-israeli-companies-from-arms-expo-over-rafah-op/0000018f-cf70-d673-ab8f-fff8e7550000</link><description>哈马斯公布以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼的录音 ■ 人质家庭论坛：内塔尼亚胡政府“做出了牺牲人质的有意识和深思熟虑的决定” ■ 由于以色列的行为，法国禁止以色列公司参加下个月举行的年度欧洲武器和国防工业展览会拉法 ■ 美国、英国军队称他们袭击了也门的胡塞武装目标 ■ 战争进入 238 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-238-france-bans-israeli-companies-from-arms-expo-over-rafah-op/0000018f-cf70-d673-ab8f-fff8e7550000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯公布以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼的录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/hamas-releases-voice-recording-of-hostage-noa-argamani/0000018f-cf59-da41-a9cf-df7f836c0000</link><description>来自贝尔谢巴的 26 岁阿伽玛尼 (Argamani) 与她的伴侣阿维纳坦·奥尔 (Avinatan Or) 一起在 Nova 音乐节上被绑架。战争初期有人看到她骑摩托车被绑架到加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 16:06:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/hamas-releases-voice-recording-of-hostage-noa-argamani/0000018f-cf59-da41-a9cf-df7f836c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女因在社交媒体上批评战争的帖子而被拘留并蒙住眼睛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-detained-blindfolded-over-social-media-posts-criticizing-war/0000018f-cee4-da41-a9cf-dffe8ad90000</link><description>警方称，以色列阿拉伯妇女拉莎·卡里姆·哈拉米因在社交媒体上发布“反以色列国防军士兵和反以色列”帖子而被捕。国家检察官办公室表示，警方在逮捕过程中的身体行为原因“尚不清楚”</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 15:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/israeli-woman-detained-blindfolded-over-social-media-posts-criticizing-war/0000018f-cee4-da41-a9cf-dffe8ad90000</guid></item><item><title>比利时根特大学与所有以色列大学断绝联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-31/ty-article/belgiums-ghent-university-severs-ties-with-all-israeli-universities/0000018f-ce8b-d117-a7ef-ffffeaa00000</link><description>根特的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者一直抗议以色列对加沙的军事进攻，并自五月初以来一直占领该校部分校园。该大学已与 3 个以色列机构断绝关系，但与 18 个以色列学术机构保持着持续的合作关系</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 12:11:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-31/ty-article/belgiums-ghent-university-severs-ties-with-all-israeli-universities/0000018f-ce8b-d117-a7ef-ffffeaa00000</guid></item><item><title>明尼苏达大学学术期刊为抵制以色列学者道歉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/university-of-minnesota-academic-journal-apologizes-for-boycotting-israeli-scholar/0000018f-ce5e-dc8d-a18f-ffdfcf520000</link><description>《文化评论》的编辑写信给一位提交论文供审阅的以色列学者，“我们遗憾地通知您，由于该期刊遵守 BDS 指南，我们无法考虑您提交的论文发表”</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 11:28:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/.premium/university-of-minnesota-academic-journal-apologizes-for-boycotting-israeli-scholar/0000018f-ce5e-dc8d-a18f-ffdfcf520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/idf-names-two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018f-ce02-d117-a7ef-ff7f99a40000</link><description>来自凯撒利亚的 24 岁中士（预备）阿达尔·加夫里尔 (Adar Gavriel) 在加沙北部的战斗中阵亡。来自耶路撒冷的 20 岁耶霍纳坦·埃利亚斯中士在加沙南部的战斗中阵亡。以色列国防军表示，在同一事件中，另一名士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 09:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-31/ty-article/idf-names-two-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-combat/0000018f-ce02-d117-a7ef-ff7f99a40000</guid></item></channel></rss>